# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in what you need.

# --- Email updates list (optional) ---
# Ona collects emails only for product updates — it does not email the result to
# the person (they download it as a PDF instead). On submit it POSTs
# { email, careerId, timestamp } to this endpoint. If unset, the address is
# stored in localStorage. Email capture never blocks the result.
VITE_LEAD_ENDPOINT=
